{"tid":2093533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超：黨安法嚇怕了加國特工 嘩卡卡卡","createTime":"2020-07-04T02:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T02:14:04.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"001962f1878ae8e418ce6fec748c84772c78b355","tid":2093533,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"李家超：加拿大要向世界解釋暫停與香港的引渡條約<br />\n04.07.2020 09:28<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大宣佈暫停執行同香港的引渡條約，保安局局長李家超在本台節目表示非常反對，他指兩國需要有機制處理嚴重案件，以保護兩地社會治安，批評加拿大是政治凌駕法律，如果加方是擔心特工被捕是理解，但港區國安法條例是針對一般罪行，希望加拿大不要忘記國際責任。<br />\n<br />\n律政司長鄭若驊亦表示極度遺憾，指加拿大做法是干擾中國內政，大大打擊兩地法治。港區國安法第38條適用於外國，鄭若驊指不少國家都有相關法例，甚至罰則更嚴，美國亦有域外管轄法例，認為如果沒有法律懲罰外國人在外國做危害國家安全的事，是講不過去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1328574&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1328574%26csid%3D261_341&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=9a6a0a9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1328574&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4a54a57d84b35fec6cc965744a5abd43cbe13589","tid":2093533,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"如果加方是擔心特工被捕是理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fc61ad75e782c6838f3a69685bf92751c94198","tid":2093533,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"比卡超你收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8696f0f9658a5867bf2b5f8c63df384c15b74c8e","tid":2093533,"uid":205884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:08:26.000Z","msg":"干預中國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79775fb27